Title: WANTED: Chief Engineer Cogwrench
Description:
Wanted for crimes against the Bilgewater Operation!

Chief Engineer Cogwrench was last seen building what appeared to be a giant spider tank on the edge of Bilgewater Beach.

Extreme caution should be used when approaching.

A large reward has been posted for Cogwrench's destruction.
ObjectivesText: Destroy Chief Engineer Cogwrench at the edge of Bilgewater Beach.
